Type The Breed Name In The Shrine & Get The Pure
Monster Rancher Metropolis: Monster Rancher Advance Archive (GameBoy Advance): Shrine Topics: Type The Breed Name In The Shrine & Get The Pure
By Lisa Shock on Saturday, December 1, 2001 - 06:32 pm:

Now, I will admit I only have access to 5 characters in the shrine right now, but, when I type in the name of a breed I know is in the game, the pure breed results. Typing "Tiger" produces a Tiger/Tiger in the shrine. I have not been able to do a lot with only 5 spaces, but, I also know that the following are not in the game:
Gali
Dino
Disc
Baku
Ape
Jill
Hare
Gaboo
Magic
Zilla
There are more breeds from older games that are not in it, I just haven't been able to try them all yet.
